Title: Gethsemane (1)
Plot: While investigating the discovery of a preserved alien body found in the mountains of Canada, Mulder is contacted by Michael Kritschgau. He tells Mulder about a government conspiracy to make people believe in aliens without question, and Mulder has been the prime target.
GuestStars: Matthew Walker, James Sutorius, Pat Skipper, John Oliver, Steve Makaj, Nancy Kerr, Barry W. Levy, Arnie Walters, Rob Freeman, Craig Brunanski
